{"tid":1433154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日記者會黑警真係認真低能","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:08:22.000Z","uid":193217,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47c7fc51c0dca31648d1fd294ef6ce730640d89e","tid":1433154,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"【警方Goodest發言】<br />\n1) 阿Sir，你自己親口認話拘捕方同學時，佢支雷射筆係未入電池嘅，咁請問你拉乜春？<br />\n無電池都可以成為攻擊性武器，方同學係發電廠？<br />\n.<br />\n2) 事經兩日，你今日都仲未知道方同學支雷射筆嘅功率係幾多，咁人地買果都唔知啦！你自己拉咗人都未攪清楚，咁你憑咩證據拉人？<br />\n.<br />\n3) 哦，尋晚尖沙咀嘅市民，你話「目測」市民嘅雷射筆係普通嘅雷射筆，所以尋晚無執法；咁方同學果支到家陣你都未驗到，憑咩當晚 「目測」你又可以拉人？<br />\n.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉貼"},{"pid":"7b15ac151dffdafc63a4c70009643e3fd0397cb4","tid":1433154,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"我唸正常人都唔會咁答<br />\n起太空館n咁多支就話無攻擊性武器<br />\n用眼睇.所以係雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n會長果支就用眼睇就係大功率<br />\n攻擊性武器.所以叫雷射槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae9d63a136a92e38ef06bb8edac70ce2c9512d2","tid":1433154,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"【圍狗屋請入！】警署聲援被捕人士有機會得不償失<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxQvkS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxQvkS</a>"},{"pid":"dac2896bd87d6955a1351f3736c999bfdb10ccc2","tid":1433154,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"屌，唔好再講個記者會啦<br />\n事實係，黃絲既班狗講乜都唔會信，藍絲既班狗話太陽係西邊升起都照信<br />\n根本就唔應該繼續浪費時間同精力去討論班狗有幾柒"},{"pid":"2afb1a45fcac472ee5f